export default function Meme(){
    return(
        <main>
            <form className="form">
                <imput type='text' 
                className='form--input'
                placeholder='Top Text'
                />

                <imput type='text' 
                className='form--input'
                placeholder='Bottom Text'
                />
                <button className='form--button'> 
                    Get a new meme image
                </button>
            </form>
        </main>
    )
}
